<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="th">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Charoenpol — Business Model: ร้านประมูลป้ายทะเบียน</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@400;700;900&family=Rajdhani:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Sarabun:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --red: #E8001D;
    --red-dark: #9B0012;
    --gold: #FFD000;
    --gold-dim: #C49B00;
    --white: #F5F5F0;
    --carbon: #0A0A0A;
    --dark: #111111;
    --panel: #161616;
    --panel2: #1C1C1C;
    --border: rgba(255,208,0,0.25);
  }

- { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }

body {
background: var(–carbon);
color: var(–white);
font-family: ‘Sarabun’, sans-serif;
overflow-x: hidden;
}

/* ─── BACKGROUND GRID ─── */
body::before {
content:’’;
position:fixed; inset:0;
background-image:
linear-gradient(rgba(232,0,29,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(232,0,29,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
background-size: 40px 40px;
pointer-events:none; z-index:0;
}

.page { position:relative; z-index:1; max-width:1000px; margin:0 auto; padding:0 24px 80px; }

/* ─── HERO ─── */
.hero {
position:relative; padding:60px 0 40px;
border-bottom: 2px solid var(–red);
overflow:hidden;
}
.hero-stripes {
position:absolute; top:0; right:-40px; width:320px; height:100%;
background: repeating-linear-gradient(
-60deg,
transparent, transparent 18px,
rgba(232,0,29,0.08) 18px, rgba(232,0,29,0.08) 36px
);
pointer-events:none;
}
.brand-tag {
display:inline-flex; align-items:center; gap:10px;
background: var(–red); color:#fff;
font-family:‘Orbitron’,sans-serif; font-size:11px; font-weight:700;
letter-spacing:3px; padding:6px 16px; text-transform:uppercase;
clip-path: polygon(0 0, 100% 0, 95% 100%, 0% 100%);
margin-bottom:24px;
}
.brand-tag::before { content:‘▶’; font-size:9px; }
.hero-company {
font-family:‘Orbitron’,sans-serif;
font-size:clamp(36px,8vw,72px);
font-weight:900;
line-height:0.9;
letter-spacing:-2px;
}
.hero-company .amp { color:var(–red); }
.hero-sub {
font-family:‘Rajdhani’,sans-serif;
font-size:clamp(14px,3vw,22px);
font-weight:600; letter-spacing:8px;
color:var(–gold); text-transform:uppercase;
margin-top:10px;
}
.hero-desc {
margin-top:20px; max-width:560px;
font-size:16px; font-weight:300;
line-height:1.7; color:rgba(245,245,240,0.75);
}
.budget-badge {
display:inline-flex; flex-direction:column; align-items:center;
background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(–gold) 0%, #B8860B 100%);
color: var(–carbon);
padding:14px 28px; margin-top:28px;
clip-path: polygon(8px 0%, 100% 0%, calc(100% - 8px) 100%, 0% 100%);
}
.budget-badge .label { font-family:‘Orbitron’,sans-serif; font-size:10px; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:3px; }
.budget-badge .amount { font-family:‘Orbitron’,sans-serif; font-size:28px; font-weight:900; line-height:1; }

/* ─── SECTION HEADERS ─── */
.section { margin-top:56px; }
.section-header {
display:flex; align-items:center; gap:16px;
margin-bottom:28px;
}
.section-num {
font-family:‘Orbitron’,sans-serif; font-size:11px; font-weight:700;
color:var(–red); letter-spacing:2px;
border:1px solid var(–red); padding:4px 10px;
clip-path: polygon(0 0,100% 0,90% 100%,0% 100%);
}
.section-title {
font-family:‘Rajdhani’,sans-serif; font-size:clamp(20px,4vw,30px);
font-weight:700; letter-spacing:2px; text-transform:uppercase;
}
.section-line {
flex:1; height:1px;
background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(–gold) 0%, transparent 100%);
}

/* ─── CANVAS / VALUE PROP ─── */
.canvas-grid {
display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:16px;
}
.canvas-grid.thirds { grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr 1fr; }
.canvas-grid.full { grid-template-columns:1fr; }

.card {
background: var(–panel);
border:1px solid var(–border);
padding:22px 24px; position:relative; overflow:hidden;
transition: border-color 0.3s, transform 0.2s;
}
.card:hover {
border-color: rgba(232,0,29,0.5);
transform:translateY(-2px);
}
.card::before {
content:’’; position:absolute; top:0; left:0;
width:3px; height:100%; background:var(–red);
}
.card.gold::before { background: var(–gold); }
.card.dim::before { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15); }

.card-icon { font-size:28px; margin-bottom:10px; }
.card-title {
font-family:‘Rajdhani’,sans-serif; font-weight:700;
font-size:16px; letter-spacing:1.5px; text-transform:uppercase;
color:var(–gold); margin-bottom:10px;
}
.card-body { font-size:14px; line-height:1.75; color:rgba(245,245,240,0.8); }
.card-body li { padding:3px 0 3px 14px; position:relative; list-style:none; }
.card-body li::before { content:’›’; position:absolute; left:0; color:var(–red); font-weight:700; }

/* ─── HIGHLIGHT BOX ─── */
.highlight {
background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(232,0,29,0.12), rgba(232,0,29,0.04));
border:1px solid rgba(232,0,29,0.4);
padding:24px 28px; position:relative; overflow:hidden;
}
.highlight::after {
content:’’; position:absolute; top:-20px; right:-20px;
width:120px; height:120px; border-radius:50%;
background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(232,0,29,0.15), transparent 70%);
pointer-events:none;
}
.highlight-label { font-family:‘Orbitron’,sans-serif; font-size:10px; letter-spacing:3px; color:var(–red); margin-bottom:8px; }
.highlight-text { font-size:20px; font-weight:700; line-height:1.5; }
.highlight-text span { color:var(–gold); }

/* ─── REVENUE MODEL ─── */
.rev-row {
display:grid; grid-template-columns:2fr 1fr 1fr;
gap:0; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
padding:14px 0; align-items:center;
}
.rev-row.header {
border-bottom:2px solid var(–red);
padding-bottom:10px;
}
.rev-row.header span { font-family:‘Orbitron’,sans-serif; font-size:10px; letter-spacing:2px; color:var(–gold); }
.rev-name { font-size:14px; font-weight:600; }
.rev-sub { font-size:12px; color:rgba(245,245,240,0.5); margin-top:2px; }
.rev-pct {
font-family:‘Rajdhani’,sans-serif; font-size:18px; font-weight:700;
color:var(–red); text-align:center;
}
.rev-est { font-size:13px; color:var(–gold); text-align:right; font-weight:600; }

/* ─── BUDGET TABLE ─── */
.budget-grid {
display:grid; gap:10px;
}
.budget-row {
display:grid; grid-template-columns:auto 1fr auto auto;
gap:12px; align-items:center;
background:var(–panel2); padding:14px 20px;
border-left:3px solid transparent; position:relative;
transition:border-color 0.3s;
}
.budget-row:hover { border-left-color:var(–gold); }
.budget-row.priority-hi { border-left-color:var(–red); }
.budget-row.priority-med { border-left-color:var(–gold); }
.budget-icon { font-size:20px; width:28px; text-align:center; }
.budget-name { font-size:14px; font-weight:600; }
.budget-note { font-size:12px; color:rgba(245,245,240,0.5); }
.budget-bar-wrap { height:4px; background:rgba(255,255,255,0.08); border-radius:2px; overflow:hidden; }
.budget-bar { height:100%; border-radius:2px; background:var(–red); }
.budget-amount { font-family:‘Rajdhani’,sans-serif; font-size:17px; font-weight:700; color:var(–gold); white-space:nowrap; min-width:90px; text-align:right; }
.budget-pct { font-size:11px; color:rgba(245,245,240,0.4); text-align:right; }

.budget-total {
display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center;
padding:16px 20px;
background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(232,0,29,0.15), transparent);
border:1px solid rgba(232,0,29,0.4);
margin-top:4px;
}
.budget-total-label { font-family:‘Orbitron’,sans-serif; font-size:12px; letter-spacing:3px; font-weight:700; }
.budget-total-amount { font-family:‘Orbitron’,sans-serif; font-size:24px; font-weight:900; color:var(–gold); }

/* ─── TIMELINE ─── */
.timeline { position:relative; padding-left:36px; }
.timeline::before {
content:’’; position:absolute; left:10px; top:0; bottom:0;
width:2px; background: linear-gradient(180deg, var(–red), var(–gold), rgba(255,255,255,0.1));
}
.tl-item { position:relative; margin-bottom:24px; }
.tl-dot {
position:absolute; left:-30px; top:4px;
width:12px; height:12px;
background:var(–red); border:2px solid var(–carbon);
transform:rotate(45deg);
}
.tl-month { font-family:‘Orbitron’,sans-serif; font-size:10px; color:var(–gold); letter-spacing:2px; margin-bottom:4px; }
.tl-title { font-family:‘Rajdhani’,sans-serif; font-size:17px; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:6px; }
.tl-body { font-size:13px; color:rgba(245,245,240,0.7); line-height:1.6; }

/* ─── KPI ROW ─── */
.kpi-row { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr); gap:12px; }
.kpi-card {
background:var(–panel2); border:1px solid var(–border);
padding:20px 16px; text-align:center; position:relative; overflow:hidden;
}
.kpi-card::after {
content:’’; position:absolute; bottom:0; left:0; right:0; height:2px;
background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(–red), var(–gold));
}
.kpi-val { font-family:‘Orbitron’,sans-serif; font-size:clamp(18px,3vw,26px); font-weight:900; color:var(–gold); }
.kpi-label { font-size:11px; color:rgba(245,245,240,0.5); margin-top:6px; letter-spacing:1px; text-transform:uppercase; }

/* ─── RISK TABLE ─── */
.risk-row { display:grid; grid-template-columns:auto 1fr auto; gap:12px; padding:12px 0; border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06); align-items:start; }
.risk-tag { font-family:‘Orbitron’,sans-serif; font-size:9px; letter-spacing:1px; padding:3px 8px; font-weight:700; }
.risk-tag.hi { background:rgba(232,0,29,0.2); color:var(–red); border:1px solid var(–red); }
.risk-tag.med { background:rgba(255,208,0,0.15); color:var(–gold); border:1px solid var(–gold); }
.risk-tag.lo { background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05); color:rgba(245,245,240,0.5); border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15); }
.risk-name { font-size:14px; font-weight:600; margin-bottom:4px; }
.risk-miti { font-size:12px; color:rgba(245,245,240,0.55); }
.risk-impact { font-size:12px; color:var(–gold); text-align:right; white-space:nowrap; }

/* ─── FOOTER ─── */
.footer {
margin-top:70px; padding-top:28px;
border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center;
}
.footer-logo { font-family:‘Orbitron’,sans-serif; font-size:18px; font-weight:900; }
.footer-logo .amp { color:var(–red); }
.footer-meta { font-size:12px; color:rgba(245,245,240,0.3); text-align:right; line-height:1.6; }

/* ─── ANIMATIONS ─── */
@keyframes fadeUp {
from { opacity:0; transform:translateY(20px); }
to   { opacity:1; transform:translateY(0); }
}
.hero, .section { animation:fadeUp 0.6s ease both; }
.section:nth-child(2){animation-delay:0.1s}
.section:nth-child(3){animation-delay:0.15s}
.section:nth-child(4){animation-delay:0.2s}
.section:nth-child(5){animation-delay:0.25s}
.section:nth-child(6){animation-delay:0.3s}

/* ─── RESPONSIVE ─── */
@media(max-width:640px){
.canvas-grid { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
.canvas-grid.thirds { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
.kpi-row { grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; }
.rev-row { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
.rev-row.header { display:none; }
.budget-row { grid-template-columns:auto 1fr auto; }
.budget-bar-wrap { display:none; }
}
</style>

</head>
<body>
<div class="page">

  <!-- ════ HERO ════ -->

  <div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-stripes"></div>
    <div class="brand-tag">Business Model Canvas 2025</div>
    <div class="hero-company">Eve<span class="amp">&</span>Earth</div>
    <div class="hero-sub">Plate Auction House</div>
    <p class="hero-desc">
      ร้านประมูลและจำหน่ายป้ายทะเบียนรถยนต์และมอเตอร์ไซค์
      เลขมงคล — เชี่ยวชาญ ไว้ใจได้ สะดวกรวดเร็ว ครบวงจร
    </p>
    <div class="budget-badge">
      <div class="label">เงินทุนเริ่มต้น</div>
      <div class="amount">100,000 ฿</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ════ VALUE PROPOSITION ════ -->

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-num">01</div>
      <div class="section-title">คุณค่าที่นำเสนอ</div>
      <div class="section-line"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="highlight" style="margin-bottom:18px">
      <div class="highlight-label">▶ CORE VALUE</div>
      <div class="highlight-text">
        ศูนย์กลางประมูลป้ายทะเบียน <span>เลขมงคล</span> สำหรับรถยนต์และมอเตอร์ไซค์<br>
        ทั้งออนไลน์และหน้าร้าน — โปร่งใส ปลอดภัย ราคายุติธรรม
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="canvas-grid thirds">
      <div class="card gold">
        <div class="card-icon">🏆</div>
        <div class="card-title">ผู้ซื้อรถใหม่</div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <ul>
            <li>ป้ายเลขดี เลขมงคล เสริมดวง</li>
            <li>จองล่วงหน้าก่อนรับรถ</li>
            <li>บริการจัดหาเลขตามความต้องการ</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon">💼</div>
        <div class="card-title">นักลงทุน/นักสะสม</div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <ul>
            <li>ป้ายหายากมูลค่าสูง</li>
            <li>ระบบประมูลโปร่งใส ตรวจสอบได้</li>
            <li>ราคาตลาด ไม่ถูกบวกแพง</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-icon">🏍️</div>
        <div class="card-title">เจ้าของมอเตอร์ไซค์</div>
        <div class="card-body">
          <ul>
            <li>ป้ายเบอร์ดีในราคาเข้าถึงได้</li>
            <li>ขายป้ายมือสองผ่านแพลตฟอร์ม</li>
            <li>บริการโอนและดำเนินเอกสาร</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ════ REVENUE MODEL ════ -->

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-num">02</div>
      <div class="section-title">แหล่งรายได้</div>
      <div class="section-line"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="card" style="padding:0 24px">
      <div class="rev-row header">
        <span>ช่องทางรายได้</span>
        <span style="text-align:center">ส่วนแบ่ง</span>
        <span style="text-align:right">คาดการณ์/เดือน</span>
      </div>
      <div class="rev-row">
        <div><div class="rev-name">🔨 ค่าธรรมเนียมประมูล (Buyer's Premium)</div><div class="rev-sub">5–10% จากราคาสุดท้าย</div></div>
        <div class="rev-pct">40%</div>
        <div class="rev-est">20,000–40,000 ฿</div>
      </div>
      <div class="rev-row">
        <div><div class="rev-name">💰 กำไรจากการซื้อ-ขายป้าย</div><div class="rev-sub">สต็อกป้ายดี รอจำหน่าย</div></div>
        <div class="rev-pct">35%</div>
        <div class="rev-est">15,000–35,000 ฿</div>
      </div>
      <div class="rev-row">
        <div><div class="rev-name">📋 ค่าลงประกาศ/นายหน้า</div><div class="rev-sub">รับฝากขาย ลงรายการ</div></div>
        <div class="rev-pct">15%</div>
        <div class="rev-est">5,000–10,000 ฿</div>
      </div>
      <div class="rev-row">
        <div><div class="rev-name">📄 บริการดำเนินเอกสาร/โอน</div><div class="rev-sub">ติดต่อกรมขนส่ง ครบวงจร</div></div>
        <div class="rev-pct">10%</div>
        <div class="rev-est">3,000–8,000 ฿</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div style="margin-top:16px">
      <div class="kpi-row">
        <div class="kpi-card"><div class="kpi-val">3–6</div><div class="kpi-label">เดือน คืนทุน</div></div>
        <div class="kpi-card"><div class="kpi-val">40K+</div><div class="kpi-label">รายได้เดือนแรก ฿</div></div>
        <div class="kpi-card"><div class="kpi-val">15–25%</div><div class="kpi-label">Margin เฉลี่ย</div></div>
        <div class="kpi-card"><div class="kpi-val">100K+</div><div class="kpi-label">เป้าหมาย/เดือน ฿</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- ════ COST / BUDGET ════ -->

  <div class="section">
    <div class="section-header">
      <div class="section-num">03</div>
      <div class="section-title">งบประมาณเริ่มต้น 100,000 ฿</div>
      <div class="section-line"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="budget-grid">
      <div class="budget-row priority-hi">
        <div class="budget-icon">🏪</div>
        <div>
          <div class="budget-name">สต็อกป้ายทะเบียนเริ่มต้น</div>
          <div class="budget-note">ซื้อป้ายมงคลพร้อมขาย 5–10 ป้าย</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="budget-bar-wrap" style="width:120px"><div class="budget-bar" style="width:50%;background:var(--red)"></div></div>
          <div class="budget-pct">50%</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="budget-amount">50,000 ฿</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="budget-row priority-med">
        <div class="budget-icon">📱</div>
        <div>
          <div class="budget-name">แพลตฟอร์มออนไลน์ + โซเชียล</div>
          <div class="budget-note">เว็บไซต์, Facebook Page, LINE OA, โฆษณา</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="budget-bar-wrap" style="width:120px"><div class="budget-bar" style="width:15%;background:var(--gold)"></div></div>
          <div class="budget-pct">15%</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="budget-amount">15,000 ฿</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="budget-row priority-med">
        <div class="budget-icon">🏢</div>
        <div>
          <div class="budget-name">ค่าเช่า + ตกแต่งพื้นที่</div>
          <div class="budget-note">ค่ามัดจำ + ตกแต่งเดือนแรก (pop-up / ออนไลน์ก่อนได้)</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="budget-bar-wrap" style="width:120px"><div class="budget-bar" style="width:12%;background:var(--gold)"></div></div>
          <div class="budget-pct">12%</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="budget-amount">12,000 ฿</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="budget-row">
        <div class="budget-icon">⚖️</div>
        <div>
          <div class="budget-name">ค่าดำเนินการทางกฎหมาย/จดทะเบียน</div>
          <div class="budget-note">จดบริษัท/ร้านค้า, ใบอนุญาต, ที่ปรึกษา</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="budget-bar-wrap" style="width:120px"><div class="budget-bar" style="width:8%"></div></div>
          <div class="budget-pct">8%</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="budget-amount">8,000 ฿</div>
        </div>
